---------------------------------------------
  GCJ/GNU Java issues
  -------------------
  
  Running the PHP/Java Bridge under GCJ ("GNU Java") is supported on Linux
  and Solaris only.  If you run FreeBSD 5.3, please use Sun, Blackdown
  or IBM java instead.

d397 1
a397 1
